      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts by a second analyst not involved in original model construction.",
      "rationale": "A peer review checklist covering geometry import, material assignment, contact definitions, boundary condition application, and post-processing was completed by an independent analyst. Three minor discrepancies were identified and corrected prior to final simulation runs. Achieved level equals required level."
